Ranger Help for: coordinate
============================

SYNTAX:      coordinate <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   8
BASE SP:     40
SKILL TYPE:  offensive

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to organize a coordinated group attack
against a target. By calling out tactical instructions, the Ranger
improves the combat effectiveness of everyone in the party for a
brief time. The bonus to the group's attacks depends on the Ranger's
charisma and skill level. This skill works best when the Ranger is
fighting alongside allies.
